Last few years my mother was suffering from health issues due to a deviated nasal septum. She was having trouble sleeping and breathing, earache, persistent cough and ringing sounds in the head. She was just going through one doctor to another and ended up doing scanning and medication, spending money without any diagnosis or root cause explained by a single doctor. She has almost given up her hopes but by god’s grace I happened to find Dr Rahul Patil through google search. By reading the reviews I thought of giving it a try. With our first visit only, he explained everything in a very clear manner.  I especially loved how Dr. Rahul Patil really took his time to explain her conditions as well as treatment options.
